a Singh( a indian wif a big bug on the head lyk manprits brother) who was bad in english went to america for a holiday...when he lie down under the sun at the beach, a local went to him and ask him,"are you relaxing?" he answered," no, i am babusingh.." then another local went and ask him the same question..he was annoyed.. so he went to another spot..he saw another Singh lying down.. he went forward and ask him..." are you relaxing(rela singh)? " the Singh answered " yes, i am" Babusingh say, " everyone is looking for you" ...                                                                                         HAHAHAHA